{"type": "article", "id": 42320, "title": "伦敦同志大游行，海报和电视广告做得都不错", "description": "这是伦敦创意机构 WCRS 发起的 Love Happens Here 项目，以纪念在英格兰及威尔士地区同性恋部分合法化 50 周年。", "date": "2017-06-23T23:07:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 1128, "name": "LGBT"}, {"id": 2059, "name": "插画"}, {"id": 5242, "name": "电视广告"}, {"id": 41747, "name": "创意机构 WCRS"}, {"id": 41748, "name": "Pulse Films"}], "category": 17, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 217, "image": "img/article/article_show/201706231411404Mh35Nsy9rUOLcew.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; text-align: justify; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>每年六月底七月初，LGBT 人士都会在伦敦掀起一场为期两周的夏日狂欢。</p><p>自 2004 年开始，<a href=\"http://prideinlondon.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">伦敦同志大游行（Pride in London）</a>都会吸引来世界各地的 LGBT 人士及其支持者，参与上万人规模的游行活动，是目前全欧洲范围内规模最大、最受瞩目的同志游行。</p><p>不过，游行只是同志狂欢节（Pride Festival）最后的高潮，在为期两周（<a href=\"http://prideinlondon.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">今年的日期：06.24——07.09</a>）的活动中，各类主题相关的演出、沙龙以及研讨会都会在伦敦发生。</p><p>为了配合今年的伦敦同志大游行，<a href=\"http://www.wcrs.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">伦敦创意机构 WCRS </a>发起了名为 Love Happens Here 的项目，以纪念在英格兰及威尔士同性恋部分合法化 50 周年，其核心活动分为两部分：一是联合Alice Bowsher，Cachetejack，Daniel Frost 以及 Jack Hudson 等 30 位插画师创作的以 LGBT 群体为主题的艺术画作，二是与英国独立电影工作室 <a href=\"http://www.pulsefilms.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pulse Films </a>和导演 Fred Scott 合作的四支电视广告。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141248CUR4GVNsP5FKj0ih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017062314124895ePzaInpsqbMkE2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>这些画作将会以海报形式出现在伦敦街头各处的广告牌、地铁站等等，四支电视广告则会集中在英国 Channel 4 播出。</p><p>考虑到 Love Happens Here 这个主题，这些插画师的创作范围被框定在一个心形图标中进行。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017062314134089WhzHUucwX6Qx5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141341UQpmri8qj5C4LPx1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141340rFgMUou74ma5dG2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141342gabzKI7ifoPHpmCk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706231413428UrLgwhqiTcaMRkO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141342oJlDqHSL6tpdCMVv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在这些海报作品中，插画师不但描绘了同性之间的爱情在伦敦这座充满包容性的城市发生的浪漫故事，亦有提醒人们关注针对 LGBT 群体仇恨犯罪的情况日益凸显的现状。</p><p>尽管每位创作者的视角、手法都不一样，但是作品中亦有不少共性：比如大面积彩虹色调的运用，以及一些 LGBT 群体想对公众说的话，比如“Gay Man,Straight Man,We’re all Human”，以及对于所爱之人的表白，比如“当我第一眼看到他，我就知道命中注定我们会在一起”等等，也被融入到作品之中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706231414200sw9KHY3rMevNEz4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141422JXPrhWqHkeg02plU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706231414233PtKkVHCTSif9L1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141423k0Jqm265jLhZUHgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141424TbnMpOAmDufhGjJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141425sZHESOktcrdBJb1i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141426zJ5iBb9aKsyMFuTw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141426Jzmvq4tQKuWNBR65.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706231414281mO2rfiDWsxXvQVu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141429KofVdZHFnC8mwSj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141431exsWlMD2ER9QrC6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141431Nycfm9EVY1quATZj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141432e5W9lJITsEKb3rOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141433jnKRYVyHf67vepca.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141433jliR6L7x5NPcs9dI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141434K9276OXtiHzf1V8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141434WybLipl6ERMS5uBs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141435vKEGfBVQnIjqmblD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141435Vd90h3t14vUrqXFH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706231414356sZvhw9J4yrbfQzA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141435Jp32zdsOjLR1qUoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170623141436p42H8ReI63k1iwtA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777624\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>而电视广告则聚焦于 LGBT 群体，讲述了一个女同性恋者、一个男同性恋者、一个双性恋者与一个跨性别者四个人的故事。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=e0517wq0rx3&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\"><a target=\"_blank\" data-sessionlink=\"feature=player-title\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=58J_at46Eoc\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bi Apology | Love Happens Here | Pride in London</a></figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z0517rqzqtb&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\"><a target=\"_blank\" data-sessionlink=\"feature=player-title\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G9bO2ErshUQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gay Apology | Love Happens Here | Pride in London</a></figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=t0517wn5phk&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\"><a target=\"_blank\" data-sessionlink=\"feature=player-title\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fDVUMMdurBc\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lesbian Apology | Love Happens Here | Pride in London</a></figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=k0517lx7dhr&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\"><a target=\"_blank\" data-sessionlink=\"feature=player-title\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0x7U5FhQTww\" rel=\"nofollow\">Trans Apology | Love Happens Here | Pride in London</a></figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/news/wcrs-pride-in-london-love-happens-here-220617\" rel=\"nofollow\">It’s Nice That</a></p>"}